org.opendaylight.controller.sal.core

Class NodeTable.NodeTableIDType

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opendaylight.controller.sal.core.NodeTable.NodeTableIDType
  • Enclosing class:
    NodeTable

    public static final class NodeTable.NodeTableIDType
extends java.lang.Object
    Enum-like static class created with the purpose of identifing multiple type of nodes in the SDN network. The type is necessary to figure out to later on correctly use the nodeTableID. Using a static class instead of an Enum so we can add dynamically new types without changing anything in the surround.
